{
  "texts": [
    "At the same time, as aforementioned in Sec.",
    "3, our mobile devices from PhoneLab are connected to a Monsoon high-voltage power monitor (AAA10F) for energy measurements, while JetsonLab supports power monitoring through SysFS probes.",
    "These metrics are buffered in memory and asynchronously persisted to the filesystem in a CSV timeseries file.",
    "As we have granular and synchronized timings for each operation of the LLM chat execution, we can correlate the power and thermal behavior of the device with the execution of the respective operation.",
    "In this section, we present results from running LLMs across devices and platforms with MELT."
  ]
}